<lyrics>[V1]
 Zan ah tuukhal an tuu an zoh, Vawlei an thut lioah, Vancungmi kha a
 rung tum i, A rung ceu an hmai ah.

[V2]
 'tih hlah,' a ti, vawlei mi hna, &quot;Lunglawmhnak thawngtha chin, Ka tum,
 ka put nannih ca-ah, Lawmhnak a tam nihin.

[V3]
 &quot;David khua ah nihin a hrin, David miphun simi, Mikhamh Khrih a simi
 Pathian, Ngakchia a hrin,&quot; a ti.

[V4]
 &quot;Puan in an hlawm hnuah an chiah, Cawkuang chungah an thlim, Nannih
 atu Amah kawl u, Nan ton lai, Ngakchia sem.&quot;

[V5]
 Vancungmi nih a chim tikah Vancungmi run an lang, Miceu micerh an si
 ngai ta, Pathian kha an thangthat.

[V6]
 &quot;Vancung a ummi Pathian kha, A thang tha bik ko seh, Vawlei ah daihnak
 tlung ko seh, Mi ca'h a vel tum seh.&quot;</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
<title>ZAN AH TUUKHAL AN TUU AN ZOH CH90</title>
</song>